== 學術泛論 ==
[[File:Lingnan_University_Campus_Overview_201410.jpg|thumb]]
嶺大於2015年獲美國《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》評選為「亞洲十大頂尖博雅學府」之一<ref name="Top 10 Asian Liberal Arts Colleges">{{cite news|title=Top 10 Asian Liberal Arts Colleges|url=https://www.forbes.com/pictures/gkle45i/lingnan-university/#6c00d45a1b5d|accessdate=2018-05-12|publisher=Forbes|archive-date=2020-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105112209/https://www.forbes.com/pictures/gkle45i/lingnan-university/#6c00d45a1b5d|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據[[QS世界大學排名|QS世界大學排名]]，嶺大在世界大學排名2018上榜並入選600強<ref>{{cite news|title=世界大學排名　港大升一級排26位|url=https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20170608/20048867|publisher=蘋果日報|date=2017-06-08|accessdate=2017-12-08|archive-date=2018-09-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180911081645/https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20170608/20048867|dead-url=no}}</ref>，嶺大於2018年[[QS世界大学排名#地区性排行榜|QS亞洲大學排名]]位列100<ref name="亞洲大學排名港大首度跌出「三甲」至第5　科大成香港一哥">{{cite news|title=亞洲大學排名港大首度跌出「三甲」至第5　科大成香港一哥|url=https://www.hk01.com/港聞/126241/亞洲大學排名港大首度跌出-三甲-至第5-科大成香港一哥|publisher=香港01|date=2017-10-17}}</ref>，香港八間教資會資助院校中有七間同時打入QS世界大學排名及QS亞洲大學排名，嶺大是香港七間同時登上兩個QS綜合排名的大學之一<ref name="QS亚洲大学排名新鲜出炉 香港高校表现亮眼">{{cite news|title=QS亚洲大学排名新鲜出炉 香港高校表现亮眼|url=http://hm.people.com.cn/n1/2017/1018/c42272-29594945.html|agency=新华网|date=2017-10-18|accessdate=2018-05-01|archive-date=2017-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171227132656/http://hm.people.com.cn/n1/2017/1018/c42272-29594945.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=2018年QS亚洲大学排名发布 中国137所高校上榜|url=http://edu.sina.com.cn/a/2017-10-18/doc-ifymviyp2093170.shtml|date=2017-10-18|accessdate=2018-05-16|archive-date=2018-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180503130712/http://edu.sina.com.cn/a/2017-10-18/doc-ifymviyp2093170.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>；學術排名方面，人文藝術位列全球212名<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/faculty-rankings/arts-and-humanities/2014#sorting=rank+region=+country=94+faculty=+stars=false+search= |title=QS World University Rankings by Faculty 2014 - Arts and Humanities |access-date=2015-06-01 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308085405/https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/faculty-rankings/arts-and-humanities/2014#sorting=rank+region=+country=94+faculty=+stars=false+search= |dead-url=no }}</ref>，哲學位列全球101-150名<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2015/philosophy#sorting=rank+region=+country=94+faculty=+stars=false+search= |title=QS World University Rankings by Subject 2015 - Philosophy |accessdate=2015-06-01 |archive-date=2015-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150929065545/http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2015/philosophy#sorting=rank+region=+country=94+faculty=+stars=false+search= |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而現代語文位列全球151-200名<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2015/modern-languages#sorting=rank+region=+country=94+faculty=+stars=false+search= |title=QS World University Rankings by Subject 2015 - Modern Languages |access-date=2015-06-01 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124042448/https://www.topuniversities.com/university-rankings/university-subject-rankings/2015/modern-languages#sorting=rank+region=+country=94+faculty=+stars=false+search= |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

